@host = https://localhost:7043

### Create Order
POST {{host}}/api/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "customer-123",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "product-1",
      "productName": "Sample Product",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 29.99
    },
    {
      "productId": "product-2", 
      "productName": "Another Product",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 15.50
    }
  ]
}

###

### Process Order (replace the GUID with actual OrderId from create response)
POST {{host}}/api/order/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012/process

###

### Process Payment  
POST {{host}}/api/payment/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012",
  "amount": 75.48,
  "paymentMethod": "CreditCard"
}
